# =============================================================================
# Docker Build Context Ignore
# =============================================================================
# Prevents Docker from trying to read broken symlinks, secrets, and other
# problematic files during `docker build .`
#
# Key insight: Docker's build context walker traverses ALL files in the
# directory tree. Broken symlinks cause `readlink` I/O errors that abort
# the entire build.

# --- CRITICAL: Symlink Protection ---
# These patterns catch common broken symlink targets in WSL/cross-platform envs
projects
Projects
external
links
mounts

